## Project Page Structure (from StormSignal.tsx)

Standard order:

1. **Hero** – `header`; back link, title, description, CTAs (`flex flex-wrap gap-4`); hero image `rounded-lg overflow-hidden border border-white/10 bg-[#151921] aspect-video`.
2. **Metrics Grid** (optional) – StatCard; `grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6`; `pt-8 pb-12`, `border-b border-white/5`.
3. **Context / Problem** – SectionHeading; body with `prose prose-invert`; `py-12 md:py-20 bg-[#0B0E14]`.
4. **Design Doctrine / Approach** (optional) – Cards with icon backgrounds (`bg-blue-500/10`, etc.); icons `w-10 h-10 rounded-sm`; `grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 md:gap-6`; `bg-[#11141a]`.
5. **Architecture / System** (optional) – Diagrams; Lane/Node for swimlanes; `py-12 md:py-20 bg-[#0B0E14]`.
6. **Case Study / Deep Dive** (optional) – `max-w-5xl`; `grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12`; `bg-[#151921]`; kicker `text-sm font-mono text-blue-400 uppercase tracking-widest`.
7. **Navigation** – Back to case studies; `py-12 bg-[#0B0E14] border-t border-white/5`.

