## Drift Issues and Best Practices

**Watch for:** Container widths (`max-w-6xl`/`max-w-5xl`), palette vs ad-hoc colors, borders (`border-white/5`/`10`), H2 size (`text-3xl`), CTA component reuse, section padding (`py-24`), motion duration (`0.6`).

**Do:** Reference Hero, About, Approach, WorkWithMe, StormSignal; start with canonical patterns; reuse components; deviate intentionally; document new patterns here.

